    // ... existing code ...
    FIRST_EDIT
    // ... existing code ...
    SECOND_EDIT
    // ... existing code ...
    THIRD_EDIT
    // ... existing code ...

    You can even write // ... remove this code ... to remove code that is no longer needed.

